{"tid":1212346,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實今日我哋要反思兩個問題","createTime":"2019-06-12T18:14:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T18:57:41.000Z","uid":160990,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8857dd01eb4c27309c1483e4c4a082fa109f1400","tid":1212346,"uid":160990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:14:42.000Z","msg":"今日發夢見到有人被情緒失控嘅狗隻襲擊，之後諗起兩個問題。<br />\n1，狗隻使用催淚氣體或布袋彈嘅時候，除咗走仲有咩方法？<br />\n2，速龍隊突進嘅時候，專捉落單嘅人，之後以武力對待，除咗走仲有咩方法？<br />\n<br />\n遊行嘅目的或衝擊立法會嘅目的，本應為成功進入立法會阻止立法會正常運作，成功突破後，佔領立法會等佢哋開唔到會。<br />\n<br />\n但係，如果衝擊成為手無寸鐵嘅人，企喺度等待狗嘅進攻之後節節敗退，咁樣有意思咩？<br />\n捉到你嘅又俾人拉，你捉到隻狗，你又夠膽好似啲狗咁打人咩？<br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得智取〉硬碰硬（企定定喺度等俾人打）<br />\n<br />\n孫子兵法：故智將務食於敵，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">食敵一鐘</span>，當吾二十鐘；忌桿一石，當吾二十石。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以明智的將軍，一定要在敵國解決糧草，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">從敵國搞到一鐘的糧食</span><br />\n<br />\n取敵之利者，貨也。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要使士兵勇於奪取敵方的軍需物資</span><br />\n<br />\n自己參透下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bccc5cf76df69d5b9e9870f0b63db4a42f3d41a6","tid":1212346,"uid":160990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:15:06.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"0514891ed5f87ad1a138902f6f40f8ae3e696588","tid":1212346,"uid":160990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:15:18.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"0dd8b5c180c0611fed1cfceddcc95aa7bcb487b9","tid":1212346,"uid":160990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:15:28.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"1b36aef954e4d712b88019c1c02c1ce901169b30","tid":1212346,"uid":160990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:15:38.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"8459844a8593f5553ef37b8776318abc95efc89b","tid":1212346,"uid":160990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:15:48.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"228053fd0c3e9cfd6466f353c91570b329d3e5de","tid":1212346,"uid":160990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:18:19.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"c4c0e0cb1159f295fef71a0bb5f1bae0f8b9cb67","tid":1212346,"uid":160990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:18:29.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"cc39e546b1c619513e45e7eb8e909bdb161e2795","tid":1212346,"uid":160990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:18:39.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"3f7b451d09808ddd7cb1167d19cca9a5d4f61bbc","tid":1212346,"uid":84511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:22:08.000Z","msg":"直接講我嘅結論先，前排同後排裝備都要齊，除非你係後勤<br />\n<br />\n之前講過，速龍副計擺到明係進攻型，係少數對少數<br />\n你會見到民警一字排開對恃嗰陣佢地係唔會出手<br />\n所以PTU發催淚彈、布袋彈嗰陣，個陣型唔好散<br />\n一散就係速龍嘅天下<br />\n我知咁講好唔負責任，因為催淚彈好難抵抗，但一定要趁啲催淚煙未出哂之前捱住再倒水<br />\n所以後排裝備一樣都要齊"},{"pid":"5b4d860d09c0b4a5a81d2a6ad0d0ecca976e3270","tid":1212346,"uid":127033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:31:32.000Z","msg":"用水淋"},{"pid":"1141ce657a3d3e9a16e237e3175cef371d280b7e","tid":1212346,"uid":160990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:56:51.000Z","msg":"仲有冇方法？"},{"pid":"ab897a46986fc78d4c14f89e8a038d09846db263","tid":1212346,"uid":160990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:57:41.000Z","msg":"諗通呢個問題，真係唔好去啦！"}]}